}}{{TIDTOC|embedded}} ==Overview== WET54G v2 serial numbers appear to start with '''BDY2'''.
(appears to be) OEM BroMax / CyberTAN (model WS635-IF) :The device is using a AC101L (AC101LKQT) PHY.
Additional FCC IDs of Q87-HGA7S-1 (Linksys HGA7S, high gain antenna) and Q87-HGA5S-1 (Linksys HGA5S, high gain antenna)
